    "body": "1. If you don't specify anything, it uses an emphemeral datadir (i.e. it gets deleted afterwards, most of the data is in-memory only). If you want to persist the `--dev` mode chain, please specify `--datadir` explicitly.\r\n\r\n2. See above, please use `--datadir`.\r\n\r\n3. No idea what Mist's solo network is.\r\n\r\n4. `ethereum_dev_mode` was a legacy mode the `--dev` flag operated. Unsure why this would be hard coded into Mist though.",
